@KoenSwinkels @MackayIM Vast majority of cases in Apr-Sep 2020 are young migrant workers.

Pre-delta (community only) : 22 / 2,343 = 0.94%
Delta outbreak I (28 Apr-11 Jul) : 7 / 943 = 0.74%
Delta outbreak II (12 Jul-22 Aug) : 19 / 3,573 = 0.53%
Delta wave (23 Aug- ): 16 / 7k (excl. active cases) = 0.23%
